{"tid":2098882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大量港豬進駐英國工作假期資訊版","createTime":"2020-07-07T22:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:12:18.000Z","uid":27251,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2b778f917b72c027cfc76a4d8315d74930caad32","tid":2098882,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T22:54:25.000Z","msg":"近日BNO消息一出，大量低能港豬湧入某幾個繁體中文書面語為主，英國工作假期資訊版作出低能發問，期間多名明顯超過三十歲港豬違反版規，以口語查問各種關於移民英國之低能問題，甚或私自發訊息向群友查問租樓買樓事儀，實在失禮，能否想像這一批白痴低能之港豬移民至英國，會鬧出不同笑話，甚至成為神枱貓屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港廢中，醒下啦屌你老母，就黎比你整臭個朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da9ff14e6f6c05f9f6728720cc96fa07d269cf7","tid":2098882,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T22:57:38.000Z","msg":"摘名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6760dc4d263c5828a4fdf48645f275b10bcb2d9a","tid":2098882,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T23:00:56.000Z","msg":"一定要有政治審查"},{"pid":"a22d3ecc7d0fcb8815320870de9ada59b4ee76a5","tid":2098882,"uid":27251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4da9ff14e6f6c05f9f6728720cc96fa07d269cf7","tid":2098882,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T22:57:38.000Z","msg":"摘名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T23:01:21.000Z","msg":"摘都摘唔晒，個台灣人群主仲好有耐性，話非常時期，幫到就幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a6c47dd5161a9daf6cb8884469d233486adc03","tid":2098882,"uid":27251,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6760dc4d263c5828